'''Julya Drusilla''' ([[Talatint|talatinit]]: IVLIA•DRVSILLA),tlul deg 16 ctumber 16  temmut di 10 yunyu 38, d yellis n Ǧermansyus d weltma-s tameẓẓyant n Kaliɣyula i yuɣalen d amenkad arumani wis kraḍ seg 28 meɣres 37 ar 24 yennayer 41 tella daɣen d tameɛcuqt-is

== Tudert ==

=== timẓi ===
Drusilla tlul deg Lalman , imi baba-s yella dinna d yiserdasen-is. Yemma-s, Agribin tamenzut terna ɣur-s akken ad s d-arew snat n teḥdayin di Lalman   ; Agribin tameẓẓyant "rran-d isem n yemma-s"  (yemma-s n Nirun )  deg 15, d Drusilla di  16. Amenkad Tibir , yusmen seg Ǧermanikusiwala-t d axeṣṣar fella-s dɣa yenɣa-t di 19

Yenna-d umazran Switun belli imiren id-bda ters tayri gar Kaliɣyula d Drusilla s tuffra ( tayri gar uqcic d weltma-s ur tettwaqbel ara di akk timettiyen ) netta tella 13 ma d netta 17 .

Yensa Kaliɣyula ɣer Tibir i seddis n yiseggasen yuɣal d awrit-is imiren tezwaǧ Drusiolla d urgaz-nniḍen

=== Weltma-s n umenkad ===
[[Tugna:Caligula_sestertius_RIC_33_680999.jpg|vignette|idrimen s udem n umenkad Kaliɣyula d yessetmas Agribin , Drusilla d Julya Livilla]]
Tibir yemmut di meɣres n 37  s tumert , yefka-as usqamu n lecyux akk i Kaliɣyula i yuɣalen d amenkad yesɛan 24 n yiseggasen. Kaliɣyula yekkas weltma-s i urgaz-is Lukyus Kasyus tebra-d deg useggas-nni yekkes-it Kaliɣyula si tudert qabel-nni .

Deg ctumber  37, yerra Kaliɣyula Drusilla d tawrit ɣef yidrimen-is d umenkud-is . d tameṭṭut tamezzwaru i wumi ara yettunefk umenkud s lebɣi n umenkad. 

Deg tuber 37, Antunya tamẓẓyant, jida-s n Kaliɣyula d Drusilla ,tenɣa iman-is, tuyes seg tudert imi yesserwa-as Kaliɣyula lemrar kkes-d d acu ur s-yexdim. Drusilla tuɣ Markus Aemiliyus Lebidus, ameddakel i yqerben ɣer gma-s.

=== Lmut ===
[[Tugna:Inscription_dédiée_par_Caligula_à_sa_soeur_Drusilla_divinisée_MBALyon_2018.jpg|vignette|tira i Drusilla yemmuten ]]
Di 10 yunyu 38, Drusillatemmut di leɛmer n 21 n yiseggasen , s tawla , i ykecmen akk ixxamen n Rum imiren .yezga Kaliɣyula ɣer tuyat-is mi akken tehlek yugi ad iwali lgifa mi temmut . S wul ihudden, yeffeɣ si Rum ur d-yuɣal armi d kra n yimalasen .

Mi d-yuɣal ɣer Rum, deg Ɣuct n 38, yessuter-d i usqamu n lecyux ad rren Drusilla d [[Yillu|illu]] , yeqqim way-a armi d Yulyus Sizar

Kaliɣyula leɛmer yeḥli seg lǧerḥ-nni , d ayen i yuaren urar ameqqran deg lehlak n tnefsit-is d tiderwect-ines i yettwasnen seg uqbel lmut n Drusilla
